        +film('Shooter', 'When you browse through videos at YouTube, which do you usually click first:', '/img/film-cover-8.png', '/film')
        +film('Going Clear Scientology', 'Attending a trade show can be a very effective method of promoting', '/img/film-cover-9.png', '/film')
